      <name>Hardeep_Tulsi</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/132334</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hello &lt;SPAN&gt;Vèche.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;In the SAP&amp;nbsp;S/4HANA system, cloud starter edition,&amp;nbsp; extensibility for key users is&lt;STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;deactivated&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;by default.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;You can activate extensibility by yourself. Open the Fiori application&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A class="" href="https://fioriappslibrary.hana.ondemand.com/sap/fix/externalViewer/#/detail/Apps%28'F4017'%29/S30" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow"&gt;Extensibility Settings&lt;/A&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;and follow the activation process.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Extensibility Settings for Extensibility Specialist&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;A href="https://fioriappslibrary.hana.ondemand.com/sap/fix/externalViewer/#/detail/Apps('F4017')/S32" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;https://fioriappslibrary.hana.ondemand.com/sap/fix/externalViewer/#/detail/Apps('F4017')/S32&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;In addition you can&amp;nbsp;&lt;SPAN&gt;enable runtime extensibility for a query in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;Custom Analytical Queries&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;app and enable business users to add additional fields to a multidimensional report. Learn more with &lt;A href="https://help.sap.com/docs/SAP_S4HANA_CLOUD/0f69f8fb28ac4bf48d2b57b9637e81fa/25ed791bbae342b1bae8451744838cad.html?version=2402.501" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;documentation&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;In addition you can learn about creating analytical queries with&lt;A href="https://developers.sap.com/tutorials/abap-custom-analytical-queries.html" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt; documentation&amp;nbsp;&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Hope this helps&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Thanks&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/enterprise-resource-planning-q-a/re-custom-analytical-queries-create-button-disabled-s/qaq-p/13655022/comment-id/4183342#M4183342"/>
